{"_path":"/maps/_person/richard-stallman","_dir":"_person","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Richard Stallman","description":"计算机程序员、软件自由运动的创始人","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"简介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简介？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Richard Stallman（理查德·斯托曼，常缩写为 RMS）是自由软件运动的发起人和核心人物之一，美国程序员与软件自由倡导者。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主要背景与贡献："}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"出生与背景"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：1953 年出生于美国纽约。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GNU 项目"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：1983 年，他发起 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GNU 项目"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，目标是创建一个完全自由（不是免费，而是自由授权）的类 Unix 操作系统。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自由软件基金会（FSF）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：1985 年创立 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Free Software Foundation"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，致力于推广和维护自由软件理念。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPL 许可证"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：他主导制定了 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GNU 通用公共许可证（GPL）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，这是世界上最有影响力的开源软件许可证之一，保证用户有权使用、复制、修改和分发软件。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"软件自由理念"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：他提出软件应赋予用户“四个自由”——运行、学习、修改和分享的自由，并强调“free”是“freedom”而非“free of charge”。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"影响与争议"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"影响与争议？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"🔹 支持者的观点"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自由与用户权利的捍卫者"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"他们认为 Stallman 是唯一始终坚持“软件自由”原则的大旗手，不妥协、不被商业利益左右。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开源与自由软件发展的奠基人"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"没有他的 GNU 项目和 GPL 许可协议，Linux 和大量开源软件可能无法迅速发展到今天的规模。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"道德与哲学启发"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"他强调软件自由是社会公义问题，而不仅仅是技术问题，这对许多开发者和活动家都有深刻影响。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"🔹 批评者的观点"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"过于理想化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"批评者认为他的理念在商业现实中难以完全落实，对企业合作有时显得不切实际。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"反对“开源”称呼的分化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"他坚持“自由软件”一词，不愿与“开源软件”混为一谈，导致部分人觉得理念过于狭隘。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"争议性言论与行为"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"他在邮件列表、演讲以及一些公共事件中的直言甚至偏激的表达方式，引发过多次舆论争议，造成部分组织与他保持距离。"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.gnu.org/philosophy/open-source-misses-the-point.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么开源错失了自由软件的重点"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"自由软件与开源软件在价值观上有何本质区别"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自由软件与开源软件在价值观上有何本质区别？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"价值观区别"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：自由软件运动强调的是用户的自由权利，包括自由运行、学习、修改和重新发布软件的自由，其核心是道德和伦理，关注的是用户的基本自由。而开源软件则更注重实用优势，如软件的强大、稳定和高效，其出发点是实用主义，关注的是软件的开发方式和质量。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"对待非自由软件的态度"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：自由软件运动认为非自由软件是一个社会问题，主张停止使用非自由软件，以维护用户的自由权利。开源软件则认为非自由软件不好是因为其开发方式劣等，但并不从道德和伦理角度批判非自由软件，甚至在某些情况下可能会接受非自由软件的某些特性，只要这些特性在技术上被认为是“更好”的。"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_person:richard-stallman.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_person/richard-stallman.md","_stem":"6.maps/_person/richard-stallman","_extension":"md"}